These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, may
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Birthday   | december | may |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, rock
1. the fan of rock is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, social-worker
1. the bartender is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| Job   | social-worker | bartender |

